Can You Recommend a Toaster?
text:
I am looking for a toaster with a specific requirement :
I want the bread-holding grid inside the toaster to be able
to handle bread of all sizes not have to go fishing for a
piece of burnt bread in the depths of the toaster. Although
it seems like a very reasonnable requirement, I have not
been able to find any one like that in Europe. 
Where else to ask if not on HN ?
